1
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,079
Eldest Young Master

2
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,200
I can't find that person who delivered the painting.

3
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:39,280
And you won't give me a hint.

4
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,840
I'm asking you one more time.

5
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,760
That thing...

6
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:45,560
should I give it to the Young Mistress or not?

7
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,200
Tell her you're not dead.

8
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Follow your heart, ask no questions.

9
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,920
If I don't ask you, how would I know?

10
00:01:58,519 --> 00:02:00,599
Is it better to let the Young Mistress know,

11
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:02,719
or better to keep her in the dark?

12
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:05,159
Think clearly.

13
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:14,120
It is heaven's will; go with the flow.

14
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,960
How am I supposed to know what heaven's will is?

15
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,039
Fan Bao.

16
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:21,680
What are you doing here?

17
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,360
Young Mistress.

18
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,039
I... I'm cleaning up.

19
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,439
What are you hiding?

20
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,719
I'm not hiding anything.

21
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:28,080
Take it out.

22
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:30,560
I said take it out.

23
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:41,879
This painting...

24
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,319
where did it come from?

25
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,719
What do I do? Do I tell her or not?

26
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:48,639
I... I painted it myself for fun.

27
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,800
This is clearly Sha'er's brushwork.

28
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:51,840
Could it be...

29
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:54,439
he also knows Sha'er is still alive?

30
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:56,840
This looks just like a love letter.

31
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:58,840
Who did you write it for?

32
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:01,080
If she recognizes it,

33
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:02,800
what should I do?

34
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:04,840
Young Mistress...

35
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,159
just don't worry about it so much.

36
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,560
Actually...

37
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,759
I know.

38
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,840
You know about me and Cuihua?

39
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,120
It has nothing to do with Cuihua.

40
00:03:18,159 --> 00:03:19,240
Say what you know.

41
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,960
I don't know.

42
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,080
You do know.

43
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,199
I...

44
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,080
Should I... should I know or not?

45
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,080
Just tell the truth.

46
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:31,599
Young Mistress...

47
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,199
How about...

48
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,919
we say it together?

49
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,439
Eldest Young Master.

50
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,360
How did you know?

51
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,240
Before he left,

52
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,479
he left me a letter.

53
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,479
I bribed the people who buried him.

54
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:48,560
Then this painting...

55
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:49,840
After all this talk,

56
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,719
the person who delivered this painting is a weirdo.

57
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,319
I only know he came from across the river.

58
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:55,240
Oh, right.

59
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,400
This painting,

60
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,879
and this jar of wine,

61
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,360
were brought by him.

62
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,280
I'm going to find him.

63
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,360
He's been gone for so long.

64
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:19,120
Who knows how much he's suffered alone.

65
00:04:19,599 --> 00:04:20,680
No matter how hard or tiring it is,

66
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:22,319
I want to be with him.

67
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,040
You have to help me think of a way.

68
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,800
What happened here?

69
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,240
Old Master.

70
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,480
A letter came from the Young Mistress's family.

71
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,879
It says her mother is ill.

72
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:44,040
So my in-law is ill.

73
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,240
You should go back for a visit.

74
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,319
Great-Uncle.

75
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,319
If I go back,

76
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,839
I don't know when I'll be able to return.

77
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,240
When that time comes,

78
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,199
what if you don't recognize me anymore?

79
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,839
Why wouldn't I recognize you?

80
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:02,040
You are my only granddaughter-in-law.

81
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,160
As long as you don't remarry,

82
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,319
in our Fan family tree,

83
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:09,000
your name will always be there.

84
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:11,959
Sha'er hasn't been gone for long.

85
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,360
If I go back to my maiden home alone,

86
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,920
and people outside find out,

87
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:20,079
who knows what gossip they'll spread.

88
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,240
Then how about this.

89
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:22,680
Fan Bao.

90
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,160
You accompany the Young Mistress.

91
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,360
What about you?

92
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,199
There are so many people in this courtyard.

93
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:30,639
What are you worrying about?

94
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:31,959
On the journey,

95
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,279
you can also protect the Young Mistress.

96
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,680
Also,

97
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,199
for the homecoming gifts,

98
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:39,399
pick some expensive ones.

99
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:39,959
Do you hear me?

100
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,839
Alright, go on then.

101
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:55,759
Cry, cry, cry.

102
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:58,680
You've been crying all night and you're still at it.

103
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,040
You've ruined my sleep.

104
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,600
If I can't sleep, no one sleeps.

105
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,079
Commander, Young Master Huo is here.

106
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,639
Take some money.

107
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,720
Send her away.

108
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,879
Remember to use the back door.

109
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:12,839
Yes, sir.

110
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,439
Sorry to keep you waiting, Young Master Huo.

111
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,519
Not at all, not at all.

112
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:20,040
You're free today, I see.

113
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:21,600
No matter how busy I am,

114
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,759
I must get the tasks

115
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,759
Commander Qin assigned done properly.

116
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:26,199
Following Commander Qin's teachings,

117
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,959
I have reluctantly parted with what I love.

118
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:28,879
From now on,

119
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,839
right or wrong, I won't pursue it anymore.

120
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,680
Good, good, good.

121
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:33,639
Please sit, please sit.

122
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,439
I told you long ago,

123
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,560
don't let that Fan fellow's silly look fool you.

124
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,759
He's actually very shrewd.

125
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,879
Otherwise, how could his business get so big?

126
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:44,160
I predict that before long,

127
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:45,800
in this godforsaken little town of ours,

128
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,759
he'll be revitalizing every trade and industry.

129
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:50,120
As the local official,

130
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,240
I am quite gratified.

131
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,959
Commander Qin, you truly care for the people.

132
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:57,720
But that Fan fellow,

133
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,680
making a fortune under Commander Qin's watch,

134
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:03,480
turns around and forgets the grace

135
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,600
of Commander Qin's protection.

136
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,360
I'm just a rough soldier.

137
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:10,199
What need have I for fame or profit?

138
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:12,519
I only want to wholeheartedly

139
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,959
serve the common people.

140
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:14,959
That's all.

141
00:07:15,839 --> 00:07:16,519
Commander Qin,

142
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,519
that's not quite right for you to say.

143
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,600
Although you, Commander Qin,

144
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,319
seek neither fame nor profit,

145
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,560
but Commander Qin,

146
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:26,279
you are always the guardian of our town,

147
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,680
the navigator, so to speak.

148
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,800
If Dongshihui lacks

149
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:33,759
Commander Qin's strategy and supervision,

150
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,639
it's likely to capsize.

151
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:39,319
Then tell me, Young Master Huo,

152
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:42,680
how should I steer this helm?

153
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,560
I suggest Commander Qin start a joint venture.

154
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,560
Take a stake.

155
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,519
I will provide the capital from behind the scenes

156
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,279
to support Commander Qin financially.

157
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,360
Then let's just

158
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:55,319
be open and direct about this.

159
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,360
How do we split the shares?

160
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,720
That's simple.

161
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,800
I provide the capital and take fifty percent.

162
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:04,399
Fan provides the technology,

163
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:05,680
give him thirty percent.

164
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:08,920
The remaining twenty percent is for Commander Qin to handle.

165
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,600
With just twenty percent,

166
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,199
I'm afraid it'll be hard to steer the helm.

167
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:17,439
Don't be hasty, Commander Qin.

168
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:20,120
He'll have to cough up his thirty percent sooner or later.

169
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:22,319
Once we get his recipe,

170
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,600
we find any excuse

171
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,560
and kick him out.

172
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:28,639
He relies on that one specialty to survive.

173
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,279
I'm afraid you'll end up in a tight spot,

174
00:08:31,279 --> 00:08:32,600
getting heat from both sides,

175
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,560
and be controlled by him instead.

176
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:37,639
That's why I have a plan in motion

177
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,600
guaranteed to get his recipe.

178
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:44,639
I won't go to your Huo family to settle the score,

179
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:46,000
which is already merciful of me.

180
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:47,320
Yet you still dare to come here?

181
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,200
Uncle Dong.

182
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,360
Who's your Uncle Dong?

183
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,399
Master Dong.

184
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:56,360
Our Young Master's invitation this time...

185
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,480
is mainly to apologize to you in person.

186
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,559
Before, there were many things

187
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:02,840
that we did inappropriately.

188
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:05,720
I hope you can be the bigger person and forgive us.

189
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,480
Like salt thrown in a river,

190
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,279
please be magnanimous.

191
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,840
Since it is an apology,

192
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,240
why doesn't he come himself?

193
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,600
Young people are thin-skinned.

194
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:18,039
He's afraid of running into Xiugu

195
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,639
and having no face to see her.

196
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,480
Now that our family is prospering,

197
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:26,039
he finally takes notice.

198
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,440
If it were like before,

199
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:30,120
would he apologize?

200
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,440
Our Young Master said,

201
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:34,399
the friendship between the Dong and Huo families can't end.

202
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,960
Even if we can't be in-laws,

203
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,360
we're still like family.

204
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:42,159
Here is an opportunity to get rich.

205
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,759
Our Young Master

206
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,399
wants to share it with those closest to him.

207
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,440
Uncle Dong,

208
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,000
this is the marriage annulment paper.

209
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,200
This is a small token of compensation.

210
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:58,840
When Xiugu was with me before,

211
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,720
fearing she might do something drastic,

212
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,279
I used some tactics.

213
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,960
I apologize to you here, Uncle Dong.

214
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,840
I've been mischievous since childhood

215
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,440
and often bullied Xiugu.

216
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:13,039
Back then, you always forgave me, Uncle Dong.

217
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,480
Now I also hope, Uncle Dong,

218
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,399
that you can be magnanimous.

219
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,440
Sit down, sit down.

220
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:27,720
Uncle Dong.

221
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:30,279
Although I hurt Xiugu's feelings,

222
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:32,559
I swear on my father's spirit tablet,

223
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,399
I absolutely did not do anything

224
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:36,559
out of line towards Xiugu.

225
00:10:39,679 --> 00:10:40,720
Little Huo,

226
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,519
it's time to grow up.

227
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,679
Yes.

228
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,240
When doing things,

229
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,360
you can't just look ahead and ignore what's behind.

230
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:51,639
You shouldn't burn your bridges.

231
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:55,159
You never know where the sun might shine.

232
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,279
Then I won't beat around the bush

233
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,799
with you, Uncle Dong.

234
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,799
Commander Qin wants to do business with us.

235
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,320
I put up the money,

236
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:08,200
and you, you provide the skills.

237
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:10,720
It's a highly profitable deal.

238
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:18,279
Making money is certainly a good thing.

239
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,799
But a partnership is a big matter.

240
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:25,399
I need to go back and think it over.

241
00:11:25,799 --> 00:11:28,080
Dongshihui is named Dong, isn't it?

242
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,559
For the boss to make a decision,

243
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:32,120
why would he need to consult the hired hands?

244
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,759
Then this boss,

245
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:36,919
is probably unworthy of the title.

246
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,120
That Commander Qin,

247
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,960
he's really excited about this right now.

248
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:43,200
You know his explosive temper.

249
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:45,399
If you make him unhappy then,

250
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:46,559
he...

251
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:51,360
will turn a good thing into a bad thing.

252
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:55,559
The chance to make it big is right now.

253
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,360
The meat is rich, and the soup is rich too.

254
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:02,960
What?

255
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:07,159
You already signed the partnership contract?

256
00:12:07,639 --> 00:12:08,639
It's business,

257
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:11,000
profit comes first.

258
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:15,200
Young Master Huo kept begging me,

259
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:18,080
he practically knelt and kowtowed to me.

260
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,320
That Commander Qin behind him,

261
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:22,120
is someone we absolutely cannot afford to offend.

262
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,840
Why couldn't you come back

263
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,240
and discuss it with us first?

264
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,720
Discuss what?

265
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:29,559
You lot have the final say on everything.

266
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:32,519
None of you take me seriously at all.

267
00:12:32,639 --> 00:12:34,000
Don't you forget,

268
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,799
Dongshihui is named Dong.

269
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:39,360
That Huo fellow is vicious.

270
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,679
Back then,

271
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,879
how he treated Xiugu,

272
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:44,799
how he treated you,

273
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,240
have you forgotten all that?

274
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:53,120
Young Master Huo has already apologized to us.

275
00:12:54,159 --> 00:12:55,360
This time the apology

276
00:12:55,759 --> 00:12:57,360
was especially sincere.

277
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:58,279
Besides,

278
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,919
I have to give his old man some face.

279
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:01,679
Anyway,

280
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:03,600
I won't work with that Huo,

281
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,759
