564
00:26:33,359 --> 00:26:33,960
Where is it?

565
00:26:34,079 --> 00:26:34,880
Which one are you asking about?

566
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:38,920
It's incredibly popular

567
00:26:39,039 --> 00:26:40,400
They've opened so many branches

568
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:41,880
It's even stirred up Chengdu Prefecture

569
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:43,400
and the officials in Chongqing Prefecture

570
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:46,039
Thank you, folks and neighbors

571
00:26:46,039 --> 00:26:47,359
Thank you all for your support

572
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:49,519
Our troops ride at full speed

573
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:50,720
transporting it overnight

574
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:52,400
The tripe served on the table

575
00:26:52,599 --> 00:26:54,400
is all fresh and crisp

576
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,680
I heard it was Boss Dong's live-in son-in-law

577
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,559
who built this up from scratch

578
00:27:00,759 --> 00:27:02,119
A live-in son-in-law

579
00:27:11,599 --> 00:27:12,839
I really never expected

580
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,799
that you'd partner with Commander Qin.

581
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,319
Only he could handle

582
00:27:16,319 --> 00:27:18,119
the ownership issue of this shop.

583
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:21,039
The key is using the army for deliveries.

584
00:27:21,559 --> 00:27:22,279
For free.

585
00:27:22,359 --> 00:27:23,960
It doesn't cost a dime.

586
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:30,039
But you're giving Commander Qin seventy percent.

587
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,119
Doesn't your heart ache?

588
00:27:32,559 --> 00:27:34,599
Franchise fees, apprenticeship fees...

589
00:27:35,079 --> 00:27:36,200
the shop's revenue...

590
00:27:36,319 --> 00:27:37,640
he takes a cut of it all.

591
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,440
Say we open a thousand shops later,

592
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:41,240
and then secure the suppliers...

593
00:27:44,319 --> 00:27:46,319
You can't dwell on the math.

594
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:50,279
I think the fiercest thing you did,

595
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:52,160
the most ruthless move,

596
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:55,200
was breaking Young Master Huo's scheme in one go.

597
00:27:55,599 --> 00:27:57,039
My flagship store is already open.

598
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,480
Why would I need his capital?

599
00:27:58,799 --> 00:27:59,759
If he doesn't invest,

600
00:28:00,039 --> 00:28:01,880
he can't get his claws in.

601
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:03,799
I didn't think that far ahead.

602
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:06,640
I just thought, asking me to work with a Huo...

603
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:07,839
absolutely not.

604
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,200
Is that so?

605
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,440
Business now...

606
00:28:14,119 --> 00:28:15,079
is so good.

607
00:28:15,559 --> 00:28:18,839
But my old potluck buddies don't come anymore.

608
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:21,799
That old hotpot was still the most comforting.

609
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:22,680
You have principles.

610
00:28:23,759 --> 00:28:25,400
You haven't forgotten your roots after making it big.

611
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,200
That's what I like about you.

612
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,480
You think everyone's like you?

613
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,680
Only caring about money.

614
00:28:34,319 --> 00:28:35,359
I do like money.

615
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:38,039
But I like talent even more.

616
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,160
Boss Fan.

617
00:28:40,559 --> 00:28:41,640
On the fifth of next month,

618
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:43,480
it's Commander Qin's 40th birthday.

619
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:46,119
Commander Qin is hosting a banquet for everyone.

620
00:28:46,319 --> 00:28:48,119
I came specifically to bring you an invitation.

621
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:48,720
Good.

622
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:50,599
As Commander Qin's partner,

623
00:28:50,799 --> 00:28:51,400
Boss Fan,

624
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,640
be sure to arrive early.

625
00:28:52,799 --> 00:28:54,079
Alright, I'll be there early.

626
00:28:59,119 --> 00:29:00,759
Using a party to rake in money.

627
00:29:01,119 --> 00:29:03,079
Commander Qin's goal is simple enough.

628
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:03,920
Easy to handle.

629
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:05,920
Unlike his superior, Division Commander Chen.

630
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:07,240
That old fox is cunning.

631
00:29:08,839 --> 00:29:09,599
You seem

632
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:12,119
to know a bit about officials.

633
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:13,480
Just hearsay.

634
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:20,160
Fan Bao!

635
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:20,759
Eldest Young Master!

636
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:23,519
Eldest Young Master! Eldest Young Master! Fan Bao!

637
00:29:23,839 --> 00:29:25,039
I finally found you!

638
00:29:25,839 --> 00:29:27,400
It really is you, Eldest Young Master!

639
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:29,839
I've had such a hard time finding you!

640
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:30,880
By the way,

641
00:29:31,039 --> 00:29:33,480
Young Mistress and the Old Master are doing fine.

642
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:34,319
That's right.

643
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,960
Young Mistress went back to her maiden home.

644
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:36,960
She can't come for now.

645
00:29:37,720 --> 00:29:38,279
Don't worry.

646
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:40,720
I haven't told anyone you're not dead.

647
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,640
Not a word, not a word.

648
00:29:41,839 --> 00:29:43,400
The Old Master and those uncles...

649
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,880
they all think you were buried alive.

650
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:48,359
So dirty, so dirty.

651
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:49,839
How did you end up like this?

652
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:52,599
They talked about some live-in son-in-law...

653
00:29:53,279 --> 00:29:54,400
was that you?

654
00:29:54,759 --> 00:29:56,319
You are that Fan Bao?

655
00:29:57,599 --> 00:29:58,279
Yes, yes, yes.

656
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,599
I... I am Fan Bao.

657
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:00,160
I...

658
00:30:04,079 --> 00:30:06,680
Did our Eldest Young Master mention me to you?

659
00:30:07,359 --> 00:30:09,119
It seems the Eldest Young Master really missed me.

660
00:30:09,279 --> 00:30:10,880
I missed you too, Eldest Young Master.

661
00:30:12,519 --> 00:30:13,720
Alright, alright, it's been a long journey.

662
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:14,759
Come in and have some good food.

663
00:30:14,839 --> 00:30:15,559
Let's go, let's go.

664
00:30:15,559 --> 00:30:16,319
I have so much to tell you.

665
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,359
So dirty.

666
00:30:17,599 --> 00:30:18,680
You were so hard to find.

667
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:20,039
I finally found you.

668
00:30:20,759 --> 00:30:22,319
Here's ten days of medicine for your mother.

669
00:30:23,319 --> 00:30:24,759
Whether there's a next batch...

670
00:30:25,599 --> 00:30:26,599
is hard to say.

671
00:30:28,319 --> 00:30:29,160
I advise you,

672
00:30:29,599 --> 00:30:30,799
like an old lady hanging herself—

673
00:30:32,319 --> 00:30:33,279
make it snappy.

674
00:30:34,839 --> 00:30:35,599
Okay, okay.

675
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,279
Young Master, no need to rush.

676
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,079
When drinking tea,

677
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:50,039
the first steep is water, the second is tea,

678
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:53,599
the third and fourth are the essence.
